&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; on 2.1-HEAD and on 2.1.2.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14274266" author="oksana danylyshyn" created="Mon, 12 Jan 2015 22:11:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;With the patch applied, I am getting values of set types successfully loaded as expected.&lt;br/&gt;
Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14274309" author="brandon.williams" created="Mon, 12 Jan 2015 22:35:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=Oksana+Danylyshyn&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;Oksana Danylyshyn&quot;&gt;Oksana Danylyshyn&lt;/a&gt; are you replacing the jar as Artem described? I notice your description says native V3, but we don&apos;t ship with cassandra-driver-core-2.1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14275287" author="Oksana Danylyshyn" created="Tue, 13 Jan 2015 14:49:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We are using the latest version of cassandra-driver-core as a dependency.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14275492" author="brandon.williams" created="Tue, 13 Jan 2015 16:30:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Alright, committed Artem&apos;s patch.  Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
